  "description": "Welcome to this beautiful 4-bedroom villa in Elviria, offering breathtaking sea views, comfort, and privacy in one of Marbella’s most sought-after locations.\n\nThe villa features four spacious bedrooms, all with built-in wardrobes. Three bedrooms have en-suite bathrooms, while the fourth bedroom enjoys a separate private bathroom, providing excellent comfort and privacy for families or groups of friends. An additional guest toilet adds further convenience.\n\nDesigned for relaxed Mediterranean living, the property boasts panoramic sea views that can be enjoyed from the indoor living areas and the generous outdoor spaces. The villa offers multiple outdoor lounge areas, perfect for unwinding throughout the day, as well as sun loungers by the private swimming pool for soaking up the Marbella sunshine.\n\nFor entertaining, the outdoor area includes a BBQ and dining space, ideal for al fresco meals and sunset dinners. A pool bar with refrigerator adds an extra touch of luxury, making long summer days by the pool even more enjoyable. For leisure and fun, guests can also enjoy a boules court and a ping pong table.\n\nAdditional features include an integrated double garage, a high-quality Bose sound system, and pool towels provided for your convenience. Dogs are welcome upon consultation, making this villa suitable for the whole family(cats not allowed).\n\nLocated in Elviria, the villa is just a short drive from Marbella’s finest beaches, renowned beach clubs, restaurants, and golf courses, while still offering a peaceful and private setting.\n\nWhether you’re looking for a luxurious beach getaway, a family holiday, or a stylish retreat near Marbella, this villa offers the perfect balance of location, comfort, and stunning surroundings.\n\nPlease note that we welcome families and couples only, no groups under 30, and no hen or stag parties. Should you fall outside of this category but wish to book nonetheless, please send us an enquiry detailing a bit more about yourself and the group that you will be travelling with so we can request this for you.",
